platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Can you get away with murder?

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You’ve got eight wickedly tense hours to get away with murder in this sublime whodunit. It’s a brainteasing delight bribing, framing, and wooing your fellow cruise-ship passengers. Should you chat up nosy Lady Honoria Armstrong or play cards with Carstairs in the smoking room? Every failed getaway encourages another try—one where you explore different areas at different times and engage in new conversations. Brilliantly written and immaculately detailed, Overboard! makes dabbling in deception great fun—and that’s the truth.
